spec_data.Name: nagios-plugins-fts
spec_data.Description:
This package provides the nagios probes for FTS3. Usually they are installed
in the nagios host, and they will contact the remote services running in the
FTS3 machines.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Mon 27 Feb 2017 05:02:44 AM EST, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Nagios probes to be run remotely against FTS3 machines
